<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0ded9da9-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s4508"><num value="4508">§ 4508.</num><heading> Amount of fellowships</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Each student awarded a fellowship shall receive a stipend which shall not exceed the cost to the student for tuition, fees, books, room and board, or $12,000, whichever is less, for each academic year of study.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id0ded9daa-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/500/s101/b/tVIII/s809">Pub. L. 99–500, § 101(b) [title VIII, § 809]</ref>, <date date="1986-10-18">Oct. 18, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/1783-39">100 Stat. 1783–39</ref>, 1783–78, and <ref href="/us/pl/99/591/s101/b/tVIII/s809">Pub. L. 99–591, § 101(b) [title VIII, § 809]</ref>, <date date="1986-10-30">Oct. 30, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3341-39">100 Stat. 3341–39</ref>, 3341–78.)</sourceCredit>
